node.text: Winter, Spring, Summer, Fall @shophighseason thru them all! I’m very excited about new things to come with @shophighseason. Follow as our journey together unfolds! It’s so odd to me, how many of my friends were imprisoned for selling weed throughout my life and now it’s a multibillion dollar industry that even still mostly excludes people that look like myself. Let’s strive to change that. Thankful to be taking part in something sure to be incredible.
